      <title>大众汽车看到大量新车型推动欧洲销量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/volkswagen-sees-slew-of-new-models-driving-sales-in-europe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大众汽车公司预计，随着德国汽车制造商更新高尔夫等热门车型，西欧的订单将在未来几个月加速增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/volkswagen-sees-slew-of-new-models-driving-sales-in-europe</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 06:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
